# ── Vercel Environment Variables ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Add these in: Vercel Dashboard → Your Project → Settings → Environment Variables

# 1. Supabase service-role key (NOT the anon key)
#    Get it from: Supabase Dashboard → Project Settings → API → service_role (secret)
SUPABASE_SERVICE_KEY=your-service-role-key-here

# 2. JWT secret — any long random string (32+ characters recommended)
#    Example:  openssl rand -base64 32
JWT_SECRET=replace-with-a-long-random-secret-string-here

# ── Notes ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# SUPABASE_URL  → already hardcoded in api/_client.js (not secret)
# ADMIN_PASSWORD → stored in the Supabase `admins` table (not an env var)
